name: 5 Dashboard templates for Figma
description:
This week freebie is a set of 5 dashboard templates released by Pixsellz exclusively for our readers. File contains a total 10 ready-made screens (light and dark modes), and provides beautifully designed components such as calendars, charts, tables, chats, and more.


It’s a great resource that you can’t miss if you need to build an admin dashboard interface, and you’re looking for inspration.


These templates are part of a bigger premium Figma design system that you can purchase for a few bucks.
